column2: # Fit a logistic regression using all feature variables via glm, and observe which predictors are relevant
# glm indicates generalized linear model and family is binomial because Sex has only F, M
modelLogisticReg <- glm(Sex ~ ., data = trainAbalone, family = binomial)
glm(formula = Sex ~ ., family = binomial, data = trainAbalone)
